---
title: Slow-Cooked Beef Stroganoff with Buttery Rice & Steamed Veggies
description: Our Slow Cook recipes are perfect for those cold nights - switch on your oven and get ready to cook low and slow to pack maximum flavour. The best things in life take time and this rather hands-off recipe will be worth the wait. Slow cook the beef in a tomato based sauce seasoned with garlic and herbs. You’ll need a soft pile of rice, stirred through in garlic butter to mop up all that stroganoff. Trust us, tonight’s dinner is one you won’t forget.

